## Font File

| File | Location | Size | Source |
|---|---|---|---|
| `noto-sans-arabic-400.ttf` | `public/fonts/` | 192 KB | Downloaded from Google Fonts static CDN |

The TTF file is committed to the repository. Do **not** rely on a CDN fetch at runtime — the file must be available locally.

If you need to re-download it:
```powershell
Invoke-WebRequest `
  -Uri "https://fonts.gstatic.com/s/notosansarabic/v33/nwpxtLGrOAZMl5nJ_wfgRg3DrWFZWsnVBJ_sS6tlqHHFlhQ5l3sQWIHPqzCfyGyvuw.ttf" `
  -OutFile "public\fonts\noto-sans-arabic-400.ttf"
```

