## File Size Expectations

| Content | Font | Expected size |
|---|---|---|
| 50-row Latin-only table | Helvetica (built-in) | 40–80 KB |
| 50-row Arabic + Latin table | NotoSansArabic TTF embedded | 200–280 KB |
| 500-row Arabic + Latin table | NotoSansArabic TTF embedded | 250–400 KB |

The font is embedded once per document regardless of row count, so size scales with rows only for the cell data.

---

## Why NOT `@react-pdf/renderer` for Table Exports

`@react-pdf/renderer` is a full layout engine (PDFKit-backed). For simple tabular data:
- Heavy bundle (adds 200+ KB to client bundle)
- Slower (layout engine overhead)
- More complex API for a table-only use case
- RTL requires manual `flexDirection: "row-reverse"` on every component

jsPDF + bidi-shaper is the correct tool for flat table exports. Use `@react-pdf/renderer` only if you need complex page layouts (multi-column, flowing text, complex RTL documents).

